{"id": "1240360398876573787", "channel_id": "1240360398876573787", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　他深入過叢林與極地，他在最高的山與最深的海下留下過足跡，他體會過至高的快樂與至苦的痛楚。他與敵人跟夥伴狂歡，他樂於嚐試所有公正與褻瀆的活動，甘苦的啤酒、酸甜的紅酒，以及鮮美的血液全不在話下。\n　　他是未知的先驅、神秘的飛蛾，引領眾人前往無法回頭的一瞬間，撲向通往地獄的烈火中。他是快樂的奴隸。```\n既然投稿角色也可以賺米，那我有很多角色可以投<:nekoinnocent:1200338279145414656> \n不過只有關雎是委託過立繪的，之後的角色就要靠AI了<:1nekotiredempty_kitty:1206774459181305956> \n\n5/17 04:00 更：把狂氣爆發的傷害自殘改成失去生命自殘，原因與更新後的圖片在[這裡](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1240360398876573787/1240756787800444968)\n\n>>>前作：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1229156600737042483", "timestamp": "2024-05-15T17:49:23.874000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-16T20:05:39.359000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "angel", "emoji_id": "1124789417308065812", "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1240360399304523916", "filename": "06b4091fc61b66df.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 111939, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1240360398876573787/1240360399304523916/06b4091fc61b66df.png?ex=69ff73a3&is=69fe2223&hm=cc1a8cadbbbbe0f8807880f6eb9120c646f8cedcd1840206c7e49e97b75e6f0b&"}, {"id": "1240360399908372610", "filename": "1e35e056e6fa9df7.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 221846, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1240360398876573787/1240360399908372610/1e35e056e6fa9df7.png?ex=69ff73a4&is=69fe2224&hm=253f60e9fcbf3d6bfb97bc3ae4693055979b15c5e407f3110e97bcad8040d4fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1240360398876573787", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原創喚醒體投稿：「冒險家」孚士德", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
